<p>In Woodland Hills more than anywhere else in the Valley, this is not optional maintenance. The heat here turns a 60% blocked vent — manageable most of the year — into a failed thermal fuse in the first week of a heatwave. Most of our Woodland Hills calls in July and August are referrals from neighbors who've already been through this exact situation and told their neighbors what to do differently. May vent cleaning. Not July emergency repair.</p>

